Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: Three Zabrak Sith of the One Sith were present at the Skirmish on Vendaxa in 137 ABY. A female wielding two lightsabers was one of the first to arrive with Darth Nihl and Darth Talon's forces.
